{
  "result": [
    {
      "id": "5949",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "1",
      "arabic_text": "سَبِّحِ ٱسۡمَ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡأَعۡلَى",
      "translation": "(1) Exalt the name of your Lord, the Most High,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "5950",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "2",
      "arabic_text": "ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ",
      "translation": "(2) Who created and proportioned",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "5951",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "3",
      "arabic_text": "وَٱلَّذِي قَدَّرَ فَهَدَىٰ",
      "translation": "(3) And who destined and [then] guided",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "5952",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "4",
      "arabic_text": "وَٱلَّذِيٓ أَخۡرَجَ ٱلۡمَرۡعَىٰ",
      "translation": "(4) And who brings out the pasture",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "5953",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "5",
      "arabic_text": "فَجَعَلَهُۥ غُثَآءً أَحۡوَىٰ",
      "translation": "(5) And [then] makes it black stubble.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "5954",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "6",
      "arabic_text": "سَنُقۡرِئُكَ فَلَا تَنسَىٰٓ",
      "translation": "(6) We will make you recite, [O Muḥammad], and you will not forget,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "5955",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "7",
      "arabic_text": "إِلَّا مَا شَآءَ ٱللَّهُۚ إِنَّهُۥ يَعۡلَمُ ٱلۡجَهۡرَ وَمَا يَخۡفَىٰ",
      "translation": "(7) Except what Allāh should will. Indeed, He knows what is declared and what is hidden.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "5956",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "8",
      "arabic_text": "وَنُيَسِّرُكَ لِلۡيُسۡرَىٰ",
      "translation": "(8) And We will ease you toward ease.[1907]",
      "footnotes": "[1907]- To the path of Allāh's religion, which is easy and natural, or toward Paradise, by giving opportunities for righteous deeds."
    },
    {
      "id": "5957",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "9",
      "arabic_text": "فَذَكِّرۡ إِن نَّفَعَتِ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰ",
      "translation": "(9) So remind, if the reminder should benefit;[1908]",
      "footnotes": "[1908]- i.e., wherever it will be heard and understood."
    },
    {
      "id": "5958",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "10",
      "arabic_text": "سَيَذَّكَّرُ مَن يَخۡشَىٰ",
      "translation": "(10) He who fears [Allāh] will be reminded.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "5959",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "11",
      "arabic_text": "وَيَتَجَنَّبُهَا ٱلۡأَشۡقَى",
      "translation": "(11) But the wretched one will avoid it –",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "5960",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "12",
      "arabic_text": "ٱلَّذِي يَصۡلَى ٱلنَّارَ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ",
      "translation": "(12) [He] who will [enter and] burn in the greatest Fire,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "5961",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "13",
      "arabic_text": "ثُمَّ لَا يَمُوتُ فِيهَا وَلَا يَحۡيَىٰ",
      "translation": "(13) Neither dying therein nor living.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "5962",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "14",
      "arabic_text": "قَدۡ أَفۡلَحَ مَن تَزَكَّىٰ",
      "translation": "(14) He has certainly succeeded who purifies himself",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "5963",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "15",
      "arabic_text": "وَذَكَرَ ٱسۡمَ رَبِّهِۦ فَصَلَّىٰ",
      "translation": "(15) And mentions the name of his Lord and prays.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "5964",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "16",
      "arabic_text": "بَلۡ تُؤۡثِرُونَ ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا",
      "translation": "(16) But you prefer the worldly life,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "5965",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "17",
      "arabic_text": "وَٱلۡأٓخِرَةُ خَيۡرٞ وَأَبۡقَىٰٓ",
      "translation": "(17) While the Hereafter is better and more enduring.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "5966",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "18",
      "arabic_text": "إِنَّ هَٰذَا لَفِي ٱلصُّحُفِ ٱلۡأُولَىٰ",
      "translation": "(18) Indeed, this is in the former scriptures,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "5967",
      "sura": "87",
      "aya": "19",
      "arabic_text": "صُحُفِ إِبۡرَٰهِيمَ وَمُوسَىٰ",
      "translation": "(19) The scriptures of Abraham and Moses.",
      "footnotes": ""
    }
  ]
}